betterf3.name: BetterF3
betterf3.description: Replaces Minecraft's original debug HUD with a highly customizable, more human-readable HUD.

betterpingdisplay.name: Better Ping Display
betterpingdisplay.description: Shows the actual ping number instead of just bars in the player list!

controlling.name: Controlling
controlling.description: Adds the ability to search for keybinds using their name in the KeyBinding menu, this allows players to easily find a key binding in the menu.

forgeconfigapiport.name: Forge Config API Port
forgeconfigapiport.description: NeoForge's & Forge's config systems provided to other modding ecosystems. Designed for a multiloader architecture.

immediatelyfast.name: ImmediatelyFast
immediatelyfast.description: Speed up and optimize immediate mode rendering in Minecraft

nochatreports.name: No Chat Reports
nochatreports.description: Strips cryptographic signatures from player messages, making it impossible to track and associate them with your Mojang/Microsoft account, as well as use Player Chat Reporting feature.

searchables.name: Searchables
searchables.description: A library mod to facilitate adding search bars with auto complete and search types.

zoomify.name: Zoomify
zoomify.description: A zoom mod with infinite customizability.

chat_heads.name: Chat Heads
chat_heads.description:
See who are you chatting with!
This mod adds player heads next to their chat messages.

continuity.name: Continuity
continuity.description: Continuity is a Fabric mod that allows resource packs that use the OptiFine connected textures format, OptiFine emissive textures format (only for blocks and item models), or OptiFine custom block layers format to work without OptiFine.

cubes-without-borders.name: Cubes Without Borders
cubes-without-borders.description: Allows you to play Minecraft in a borderless fullscreen window.

dynamic_fps.name: Dynamic FPS
dynamic_fps.description: Reduce resource usage while Minecraft is in the background or idle.

entity_model_features.name: Entity Model Features
entity_model_features.description:
This is an expansion of the ETF mod, it adds support for OptiFine format Custom Entity Model (CEM) resource packs.
While still allowing you to disable this to use a different model mod :)

entity_texture_features.name: Entity Texture Features
entity_texture_features.description:
Adds support for resource-pack driven features for entity textures including some OptiFine features
Supports OptiFine:
 - Random & Custom textures
 - Emissive textures
With more features such as:
 - Blinking textures
 - Player Skin support

entityculling.name: EntityCulling
entityculling.description: This mod uses async path-tracing to hide Tiles/Entities that are not visible.

fabric-api.name: Fabric API
fabric-api.description: Core API module providing key hooks and intercompatibility features.

firstperson.name: FirstPerson
firstperson.description: Enables the third person Model in firstperson

iris.name: Iris
iris.description: A modern shaders mod for Minecraft intended to be compatible with existing OptiFine shader packs

lambdynlights.name: LambDynamicLights
lambdynlights.description: The most feature-complete dynamic lighting mod for Fabric.

languagereload.name: Language Reload
languagereload.description: Reduces load times and adds fallbacks for languages.

lithium.name: Lithium
lithium.description: Lithium is a free and open-source optimization mod for Minecraft which makes a wide range of performance improvements to the game.

melody.name: Melody
melody.description: OpenAL-based library mod to play background music.

modelfix.name: Model Gap Fix
modelfix.description: Removes small gaps in item and block models

modmenu.name: Mod Menu
modmenu.description: Adds a mod menu to view the list of mods you have installed.

placeholder-api.name: Placeholder API
placeholder-api.description: Simple api for mods allowing for user friendly formatting and universal placeholders!

rrls.name: Remove Reloading Screen
rrls.description: Makes resource packs load in the background, allowing you to do other things while waiting!

skinlayers3d.name: 3d-Skin-Layers
skinlayers3d.description: Renders the player skin layer in 3d

sodium-extra.name: Sodium Extra
sodium-extra.description: Features that shouldn't be in Sodium.

sodium.name: Sodium
sodium.description: Sodium is a powerful rendering engine for Minecraft which greatly improves frame rates and micro-stutter, while fixing many graphical issues

yet_another_config_lib_v3.name: YetAnotherConfigLib
yet_another_config_lib_v3.description: YetAnotherConfigLib (yacl) is just that. A builder-based configuration library for Minecraft.

nuit.name: Nuit
nuit.description: Adds custom skybox support to Minecraft

sbcou-core.name: Sbcou
sbcou-core.description:
The description of your mod. 
Accepts multilines.

sbcou-dev-gui.name: Sbcou
sbcou-dev-gui.description:
The description of your mod. 
Accepts multilines.

animatica.name: Animatica

enhancedblockentities.name: Enhanced Block Entities

fabricskyboxes.name: FabricSkyBoxes
fabricskyboxes.description: Adds custom skybox support to MC

modernfix.name: ModernFix
modernfix.description: Egregious, yet effective performance improvements for modern Minecraft

screenshotclipboard.description: Any time you take a screenshot in the game, the image data is copied to the clipboard. You can then paste this anywhere (e.g. Discord) to upload the image and share it with others.

toomanybinds.name: Too Many Binds
